rows.label: qst701405_msg0001
rows.name:
Now, let's see how effective
Kagutsuchi's Pestronella Oil is...

rows.label: qst701405_msg0002
rows.name: Hikari, try walking over there for me.

rows.label: qst701405_msg0003
rows.name: Heh...?

rows.label: qst701405_msg0004
rows.name: N-No thank you.

rows.label: qst701405_msg0005
rows.name:
It's not that I don't
trust Kagutsuchi, but...

rows.label: qst701405_msg0006
rows.name:
It would be the worst if I got
swarmed by those creepy things.

rows.label: qst701405_msg0007
rows.name: ...I'll go.

rows.label: qst701405_msg0008
rows.name: Shin...

rows.label: qst701405_msg0009
rows.name:
It should work, but be
careful just in case.

rows.label: qst701405_msg0010
rows.name: Yeah...

rows.label: qst701405_msg0011
rows.name:
Hey, are you really
confident this will work?

rows.label: qst701405_msg0012
rows.name:
I made it exactly according
to the recipe in my diary.

rows.label: qst701405_msg0013
rows.name:
However, the diary's recipe was
written by my past self, and it's
not guaranteed to be correct.

rows.label: qst701405_msg0014
rows.name: So, the probability is fifty-fifty.

rows.label: qst701405_msg0015
rows.name: Ehh...?

rows.label: qst701405_msg0016
rows.name: It seems to be working.

rows.label: qst701405_msg0017
rows.name: We did it...

rows.label: qst701405_msg0018
rows.name:
The recipe was correct.
Good job, my past self.

rows.label: qst701405_msg0019
rows.name: I see... You're welcome.

rows.label: qst701405_msg0020
rows.name:
Well then, let's go back and give
this Pestronella Oil to Ivan.

rows.label: qst701405_msg0021
rows.name:
He's probably waiting, so
we should hurry back to
the Orem Storage Ward.
